title: Wrangler Men's Premium Performance Cowboy Cut Regular Fit Jeans
description: REGULAR FIT. Designed with a functional fit in mind, these jeans are made to stack over your favorite pair of boots. Constructed with a regular fit in the waist, seat, and thigh, this jean is made for both function and comfort for long days in the saddle.

CLASSIC COWBOY JEAN. Made for the original cowboys, this classic cowboy cut jean has an authentic design that is tried and true. This western denim essential will stay with you for years to come and maintain that timeless cowboy style.

PREMIUM PERFORMANCE. Whether you're riding a bull or working on the ranch, you need a premium performance jean built for comfort and breathability. Made with a comfort waist, these jeans will keep you comfortable throughout the day.

DURABLE MATERIALS. It's no question that this premium performance jean can withstand wear and tear. Built with durable heavyweight cotton and felled seams for added comfort, this regular fit jean was made to last -- no matter the task.
FIVE POCKET STYLING. This cowboy cut jean is constructed with deep pockets and a roomier watch pocket for easier storage. Finished with copper rivets for added long-lasting durability.
Wrangler Mens Premium Performance Cowboy Cut Regular Fit Jeans
